## Prerequisites

To view the grafana dashboards below, you will need the following.

- `@justice.gov.uk` account.
- Be a member of the `MoJO-EntApp-Grafana_Viewer` AzureAD group.
- Slack access which is available to any `@justice.gov.uk` or `@digital.justice.gov.uk` account. Request via [support portal](https://mojprod.service-now.com/)

